<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card">
    <h1>About Me</h1>

    <hr>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
    <%= image_tag "Hunter3.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: 'profile-img' %>

   <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
          
            <div class="skill">
              <h4><%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div
                  class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning"
                  role="progressbar"
                  aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_utilized %>"
                  aria-valuemax="100"
                  style="width: <%= skill.percent_utilized %>%"
                ></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>
 <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>   I am a problem solver. I try to be the best developer I can be, and strive in leadership and creative problem solving. My goal is to create your story with clean code and integrity. Not just a programmer, but a problem solver. </p>

        <p> Other hobbies besides coding include traveling, reading, and writing about whatever comes to mind. 

        
        <p>
          <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#jobHistory"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="jobHistory"
          >
            Job History
          </button>
 <button
            class="btn btn-primary"
            type="button"
            data-toggle="collapse"
            data-target="#education"
            aria-expanded="false"
            aria-controler="education"
          >
            Education
          </button>
        </p>

        <p>
          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 1
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              Job 2
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="collapse" id="education">
            <div class="card card-block">
              Bottega Tech
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              UVU
            </div>
            <div class="card card-block">
              SUU
            </div>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>